data.title: Princess Madeleine of Sweden - Latest news, views, photos, gossip and video
data.meta_description: Get the latest news on Princess Madeleine of Sweden from MailOnline.
data.text:
Forget the frumpy silhouette, it's warmth that counts when the royals are out and about - which is why they've given their seal of approval to the humble padded jacket, writes ELIZA SCARBOROUGH

Serving both function and fashion, the royals use this cold-weather staple in myriad styles. Some might bemoan the frumpy silhouette of the classic padded jacket - but it's stylish all the same.

Princess Madeleine of Sweden posts throwback snaps a week after King Carl XVI Gustaf's 50th Jubilee to share the 'special moments'

Following her father's 50th Jubilee last week, Princess Madeleine of Sweden has shared 'a few special moments' from the royal celebrations on her Instagram account.

Prince Oscar steals the show again! Swedish royal, seven, looks adorable as he waves from royal balcony to mark grandfather King Carl XVI Gustaf's Jubilee (but cousin Alexander gives him a run for his money!)

Prince Oscar of Sweden , seven, adorably won over crowds as joined his family to celebrate his grandfather's Golden Jubilee celebration in Stockholm, for the second day in a row.

A GOLDEN celebration! Queen Silvia of Sweden dons glittering gown as she joins fellow European royals to mark her husband King Carl Gustaf's 50 years on the throne

Queen Silvia of Sweden donned a glittering golden gown as she joined her fellow European royals to mark her husband King Carl Gustaf's 50 years on the throne tonight.

Giving Louis a run for his money! Prince Oscar of Sweden, seven, steals the show as he joins his family on the balcony at King Carl Gustaf's Golden Jubilee celebration

Prince Oscar of Sweden, seven, joined his family to celebrate his grandfather King Carl Gustaf's Golden Jubilee celebration in Stockholm today.

Swedish royals arrive in style for religious service giving thanks for King Carl Gustaf as they celebrate his Golden Jubilee

Carl Gustaf , 77, appeared to be in a merry spirit while arriving at the Royal Palace Church in Stockholm to celebrate his 50th anniversary on the throne.

Swedish royals including Crown Princess Victoria and Princess Sofia put on a dazzling display as they mark King Carl Gustaf's Golden Jubilee

The Swedish royal family put on a glittering display as they arrived for King Carl Gustaf's Golden Jubilee celebration in Stockholm today.

Is THIS the reason Princess Madeleine is moving her family back to Sweden? Fans speculate she 'wants to keep children in line of succession' with the move

Blogger Gert's Royals posted on Twitter explaining the Swedish royal family's rules stipulate children must be educated in Sweden to remain in the line of succession.

Royals coming home! Princess Madeleine and her family will return to Sweden 'indefinitely' this autumn after 10 years in the US

The Swedish royal, 40, and her husband Chris O'Neill will move to Stockholm 'indefinitely' in August, in time for their youngest daughter Adrienne to begin school.

A royal trick or treat! Princess Madeleine of Sweden shares a family snap of her children dressed up for Halloween - after taking them pumpkin picking

The mother-of-three, 40, who lives in Miami, posted a new portrait with Leonore, eight, Nicolas, seven, and Adrienne, four, to her official Instagram account yesterday.

Taking style tips from Kate? Princess Madeleine of Sweden replicates the Duchess of Cambridge's Christmas look in a black sweater and red check midi skirt

Madeleine stepped out with her husband and three children to take part in an annual royal tradition which saw them receive the Royal Palace in Stockholm's official Christmas trees.

Too much for some! Prince Nicolas of Sweden, 6, takes a nap on his dad's lap while his mum Princess Madeleine and grandparents enjoy a dance during family outing to a concert

Princess Madeleine, 39, appeared in great spirits as she danced during a performance at Solliden Sessions near Borgholm on Saturday 10 July, while her husband Chris remained seated.

Crown Princess Madeleine of Sweden shows off her summer lockdown style in a floral gown as she poses in a tropical garden for new portrait released to mark her 38th birthday

Crown Princess Madeleine of Sweden, 38, donned a stunning floral gown as she posed in a tropical garden at her home in Miami in a new portrait released to mark her birthday yesterday.

Happy birthday Princess Leonore! Madeleine of Sweden shares adorable unseen snap of her daughter as she turns five

Madeleine's eldest child, who is eighth in line to the Swedish throne, turns five today and is expected to celebrate the occasion in private with her family.

Royally glamorous! Sweden's Princess Madeleine dazzles in sequins as she joins her brother Carl Philip and their parents at a charity gala in Stockholm

The Royal Family of Sweden attended the charity dinner of the World Childhood Foundation's 20th anniversary at Tivoli Grona Lund, Stockholm, Sweden, last night.

A royal trick or treat! Princess Madeleine of Sweden dresses up for Halloween with children Leonore, four, Nicolas, three, and baby Adrienne - as the family embrace life in the US

Madeleine, 36, wore a black cat costume as she and Leonore, four, Nicolas, three, and baby Adrienne celebrated their first Halloween in Miami together. The royal shared the snap on Instagram.

Scandi summer! Princess Madeleine of Sweden posts an adorable photo of her daughter Princess Leonore, four, deep in concentration on a fishing trip

The royal, 36, managed to enjoy some quality time with her eldest daughter Princess Leonore, four, on a fishing trip this weekend, and took to Instagram to share pictures of their trip to the Swedish coast.

Princess Madeleine serves as a bridesmaid as Sweden's royals turn out in force for her friend's wedding - but Princess Sofia almost upstages the bride in a glamorous yellow gown

Princess Madeleine of Sweden served as a bridesmaid for her best friend Louise Gottlieb when she tied the knot with Gustav Thott at Holo Church in Sdermanland on Saturday.

Already an Instagram star! Madeleine of Sweden shares a series of adorable snaps to celebrate Princess Adrienne's first week of life

Doting mother Princess Madeleine has just joined Instagram and couldn't resist the opportunity to post a selection of sweet snaps to mark Princess Adrienne's first week of life.

Introducing Princess Adrienne! Madeleine of Sweden reveals her newborn daughter's name - and shares a sweet snap of the little royal bonding with her brother and sister

Princess Madeleine of Sweden, 35, used her new Instagram account to announce her newborn daughter's name this morning - Adrienne Josephine Alice, the Duchess of Blekinge.

It's a royal baby boom! Sweden's Princess Madeleine is now a mother-of-three after giving birth to a girl weeks before Kate's due date

Princess Madeleine of Sweden, 35, and her American husband Chris O'Neill welcomed a baby girl, weighing 3.4kg, in the early hours of this morning at Danderyd Hospital in Stockholm.

'We look forward to four becoming five': Princess Madeleine of Sweden announces she's expecting her third child with husband Chris O'Neill

Princess Madeleine of Sweden, 35, has taken to her official Facebook page to announce she's expecting her third child with her financier husband Chris O'Neill, due in March 2018.

'You make us smile every day': Madeleine of Sweden celebrates Princess Leonore's third birthday with adorable portraits of the young royal playing with balloons

Princess Madeleine of Sweden, 34, has released adorable portraits of her daughter Leonore to celebrate her third birthday, showing the young princess playing with balloons.

The prairie princess: Stylish Madeleine of Sweden looks pretty in a peasant blouse as she opens a childrens library in London

Princess Madeleine of Sweden, pictured, looked radiant in the soft cream blouse, which featured delicate floral embroidery and a short floaty cape as she opened a children's library in London today.

Her snow angels! Princess Madeleine of Sweden shares adorable pictures of her children frolicking in the snow in Verbier

The candid pictures of Princess Leonore, two, and 19-month-old Prince Nicolas, are believed to have been taken during a family skiing holiday in Verbier, Switzerland.

'We'd love a play date': Princess Madeleine of Sweden reveals she hopes her children can bond with George and Charlotte

Princess Madeleine of Sweden, 34, has revealed that she'd love her children Nicolas, 15 months, and Leonore, two, to have a royal play date with Prince George and Princess Charlotte.

Heartwarming photos capture the moment Princess Madeleine and Queen Silvia of Sweden make a seriously ill girl's dream come true - by taking her on a tour of the Royal Palace

After Prince Alexander's christening this weekend, Princess Madeleine and Queen Silvia returned to their charity work, offering a palace tour to seriously ill 7-year-old Enna, from Skane.

'We love you to the moon and back': Princess Madeleine of Sweden marks her son Nicolas's first birthday with super-cute photos and a touching message

Prince Nicolas of Sweden turns one today and the Swedish royals have released new portraits of the young prince. Wearing a checked blue shirt, Nicolas looks more of a toddler than a baby.

Princess Madeleine steals the show! Glamorous Swedish Royals dazzle on way to the opera to celebrate King Carl XVI Gustaf's 70th birthday

The King of Sweden arrived at the opera in a horse-drawn carriage accompanied by his wife and a host of glamorous Swedish royals celebrating his 70th birthday.

Blue-eyed boy! Princess Madeleine of Sweden shares a precious picture of nine-month-old Prince Nicolas, noting that time has been 'flying' since his birth

Princess Madeleine of Sweden said 'time is flying' as she shared a new picture of her nine-month-old son Prince Nicolas. The royal lives in London with husband Chris O'Neill, 41, and their two children

Sunkissed Princess Madeleine of Sweden is the ultimate beach babe as she poses with her adorable children on Maldives beach holiday

The Swedish princess plays with her children, Princess Leonore, one, and seven-month-old Prince Nicolas, in the pictures she posted on Facebook from the Maldives.

'My little angels!' Proud mother Princess Madeleine of Sweden shares touching family photos featuring daughter Leonore and newborn Prince Nicolas

The photos were released by the Swedish Royal Court and show proud mother Madeleine cradling her six-week-old son Prince Nicolas. The snaps were taken at Solliden Palace on land Island.

Meet the latest Swedish royal: First picture of Princess Madeleine's newborn son is released as big sister and a very proud daddy pay a visit to the maternity ward

Princess Madeleine and her husband Christopher O'Neill have released the first image of their second child, who was born in Stockholm on Monday afternoon.

Sweden gets ANOTHER new royal: Princess Madeleine gives birth to a son - two days after brother Carl-Philip married ex-glamour model Sofia Hellqvist

According to a statement released by the Swedish Royal Court, the 33-year-old gave birth to a baby boy at 13.45 local time (11.45 GMT). Mother and child are thought to be doing well.
